videos.description: Rui Hachimura drives to the basket and slams down a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Hachimura throws down a hammer

videos.description: Gonzaga's Corey Kispert receives a long pass, and hits a lay-in while drawing a foul.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' Kispert drives in for nice layup

videos.description: Zach Norvell Jr. receives a quick pass from Josh Perkins and makes a 3-point jumper.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Norvell drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Josh Perkins drains an off-balance three-pointer from the wing.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Perkins swishes 3-pointer

videos.description: Mohamed Bamba gets the rebound slams it in before the halftime buzzer.
videos.headline: Texas' Bamba dunks seconds before buzzer

videos.description: Bulldogs' head coach Mark Few talks about the Zags' 24-0 run, and how they need to stop turning the ball over.
videos.headline: Few discusses Gonzaga's 24-0 run

videos.description: Josh Perkins lobs the ball to Rui Hachimura who makes the layup.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' Hachimura lays it in

videos.description: Corey Kispert makes a steal and takes it to the basket for a reverse layup.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Kispert goes coast-to-coast

videos.description: Killian Tillie goes for a layup, and his shoes gets caught on defender's jersey.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Tillie hits the floor hard

videos.description: Andrew Jones closes the gap with Gonzaga on a 3-pointer from the wing.
videos.headline: Texas' Jones drills 3-pointer

videos.description: Back-to-back Bulldog turnovers make it a 9-point game.
videos.headline: Sloppy series of events by Gonzaga

videos.description: Josh Perkins draws in the defenders and finds Killian Tillie who drains a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Great pick-and-roll action from Bulldogs

videos.description: Silas Melson gets the ball from a deflection and sinks a 3-point jumper.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Melson drains 3 as shot clock expires

videos.description: Bulldogs' Josh Perkins makes a bad pass that leads to Longhorns' game-tying 3-pointer by Andrew Jones.
videos.headline: Errant Gonzaga pass leads to OT

videos.description: Longhorns' Mohamed Bamba turns the ball over which leads to Johnathan Williams finishing the play with a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Texas turnover leads to Gonzaga dunk

videos.description: Silas Melson steals the ball and goes coast-to-coast to make a layup and seal a victory for No. 17 Gonzaga over Texas.
videos.headline: Gonzaga finishes off Texas in style

videos.description: Josh Perkins talks about his bad inbounds pass, and how his teammates helped him.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' Perkins discusses mistakes in OT

videos.description: Gonzaga teammates and roommates Josh Perkins and Corey Kispert discuss life on the road and living with each other. Head coach Mark Few chimes in on Perkins' wardrobe.
